      <h2>We are <span>handcrafters</span></h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3>Product Development</h3>
          <p>If you have nothing more than an idea, we'll help you develop it and bring it to life as an MVP. We'll even stand side by side with you as we carry it to a full blown product.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
