          <p>Group Buddies is the name Web is our game. We'll build pretty much anything you want as long as it is on the web.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>User Interface Design</h3>
          <p>If you have a product already online but you feel that it needs revamping, or you have the coding skills but your awesome product is not as catching to the eye as you believe it should be, we'll help you out.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
